A troll is a member of a race of rubbery-skinned grayish-green 
humanoid carnivores which most people find truly repugnant and 
fearsome.  Trolls usually stand about eight feet tall, and have dirty 
claws and pointed teeth.  Their arms and legs are long and ungainly-
looking.  They are very strong and can take alot of damage, but are 
dim-witted and lacking intelligence.  In combat, they sometimes rip 
gobbets of flesh off their opponents to eat while continuing to fight.

Trolls regenerate hit points and spell points faster than the other races.
 
Trolls cannot join the following guilds:  Bard, Charlatan, Cleric of
Mitra, Mage, Necromancer, Paladin, Psionicist, Swashbuckler, Thief.
